title: Studio Apartment for rent
posting_body: ['Unfurnished studio apartment available for rent as of September 1st 2022.', 'The studio is facing the East River on the 13th floor for $2100/month.', 'Utilities included.', 'Tenant arranges and pays their own internet and cable services.', 'Windsor Tower is a full service, 24/7 doorman building with concierge services, convenience store in Lobby, Laundry Room, Updated Fitness Center and Community Room.', 'Bike and regular storage available.', 'Conveniently located close to Grand Central and near MTA bus and express lines, Tudor City is a hidden oasis of green – a North and South Park seated on a hill near the United Nations', '2 closets; including 1 walk-in closet', 'This building does not allow smoking', 'This building does not allow renters to have pets.', "If you meet the co-op's basic financial criteria (below), please let us know when you would like to view.", '• Do you have a good credit score?', '• Can you provide a reference letters from most recent landlord?', '• No pets or smokers per co-op.', '• Heat, electricity, water and a/c included.', 'Approximately 10 business days to process application, verified annual income equal to approximate monthly rent x40, , 12 month lease; guarantors on a case by case basis.', 'If you are interested in viewing the apartment, please contact Izzy 917-374-4340.']
